Let&#39;s say your `JAVA_HOME` points to JDK7 (which will run maven processes)

Your `pom.xml` could be : 

    &lt;build&gt;
        &lt;plugins&gt;
            &lt;!-- we want JDK 1.6 source and binary compatiblility --&gt;
            &lt;plugin&gt;
                &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;
