      &lt;/profiles&gt;
      [...]
      &lt;activeProfiles&gt;
        &lt;activeProfile&gt;compiler&lt;/activeProfile&gt;
      &lt;/activeProfiles&gt;
    &lt;/settings&gt;

  [1]: http://maven.apache.org/plugins/maven-compiler-plugin/examples/compile-using-different-jdk.html

